oracle.xml.xquery

Interface OXQStackTraceVariable


  •  
    public interface OXQStackTraceVariable
    Provides information about a variable binding in addition to what is provided by XQStackTraceVariable.
    Since:
    12.1
    See Also:
    OXQStackTraceElement
